snippet.title: Axiom Soccer Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Take control of a precision-engineered drone built with a singular purpose - to score goals!

Axiom Soccer is a fresh take on future sport. The stadium and the crowds, the spectacular shots, saves and goalmouth drama – they are all there, but now high-tech, projectile-firing drones pursue sporting glory.

Axiom Soccer on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/903730/Axiom_Soccer/

Sign up for our exclusive beta! https://www.axiomsoccer.com/
